reviewText: Both movies were packed with action.  Good story lines.  Actually, two of Seagal's better movies.  I had to re-watch them so I didn't miss any of the action.  Good stuff.
I love Steven Seagal and I buy any/every movie of his that I can.  Some I do not like as well as others, but enjoy them anyway.  These 2 are good movies.
YES ANOTHER TWO MOVIES FOR CHEEP. CAN NOT BEAT THE PRICE.. GREAT SHAPE.I AM COLLECTING ALL HIS MOVIES... GREAT GREAT
We're Seagal fans ! We love the action in his movies. Wouldn't want young kids watching due to violence. thanks
the only thing i can say is if you are a big fan of stevens then go for it plus you get 2 for a good price and if your not a fan i say buy it the movie is still good
